ElasticSinkConnector - Class in sink
ElasticSinkConnector implements the connector interface to retrieve csv data from Kafka, convert them to JSON format using a mapping file, and stores them in the appropriate index in Elastic.

ElasticSinkTask - Class in sink
ElasticSinkTask is a Task that receives raw and preprocessed netflow data in csv format, converts them to json format and stores them to Elastic.
